{
  "levelId": "forest-03",
  "chapterId": "forest-03",
  "worldId": "forest",
  "title": "树屋邮局：送出信件",
  "rewards": {
    "growthPoints": 5
  },
  "scenes": [
    {
      "sceneId": "post",
      "background": "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/scenes/forest/forest-03.webp",
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "树屋邮局的风把信纸吹得满天都是。每封信都写着一个朋友的名字。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "这里就是树屋邮局。我们先把“送出信件”记在地图上。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我闻到了叶子和雨水的味道，森林朋友就在附近。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "先听树叶的声音，再用温柔的动作帮助这里的朋友。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "activity",
          "activityType": "route",
          "prompt": "把发光的信件送到对应的树屋信箱。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "right",
          "actions": [
            {
              "label": "送到红叶信箱",
              "feedback": "小松鼠收到了信，尾巴开心地转圈。"
            },
            {
              "label": "送到蓝花信箱",
              "feedback": "小青蛙收到了信，溪水响起了欢迎声。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "小小探险家完成了第一步，送到红叶信箱让周围的线索变得清楚起来。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "看！刚才藏起来的线索露出来了。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "轻轻完成这一步，藏在叶影里的小路出现了。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "把这条小路和森林地图连起来，萤光就会为我们领路。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "记住这片叶子的形状，下一次遇见它就知道该往哪里走。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "‘信’是把心里的话送给远方的朋友。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "right"
        }
      ],
      "sceneAssets": {
